    <briefdescription>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This class allows progress to be reported from different threads. Unlike progress callback that is passed to <ref refid="group__BasicGroup_1gaf184f372f735726148d7a07cbbbb29af" kindref="member">ParallelFor</ref>, each task may report the progress separately, and the progress displayed to user is not just a number of completed tasks divided by the total number of tasks, but rather a (weighted) average of progresses reported from each task </para>
    </detaileddescription>
